reviewText: Not happy, it was the right case but wrong DVD inside it
If you can't go hear him, buy the video, or if all else fails, read the book.
I met Mr Harrision once, and he is as interesting on this film as he was in person.  This is a great insight into Old Florida life as my grandparents lived it.

This is a great video, entertaining and educational... I've lived in  SW  Florida 12 yrs and had no clue of it's wonderful
cowboy history.
